text: If your only income is your W2 job, you are one bad season away from having no income and being poor. Bad approach. Think about your skill sets. Go do Uber, go do Uber eats. Think about different skill sets that you have that you can use to make money. That is probably one of the most important things you can do to really increase your savings overall is not just rely on your day to day income, but find other ways to do this.
